    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《星期一综合症》是一款单人动作类Roguelike游戏，你将扮演一名被困在地狱般办公室的实习生。 深入讽刺意味十足的公司地狱，用由办公用品改装成的奇葩武器，与恶魔化的同事们展开激战，在无尽、程序生成的高楼中奋力求生。你能撑过这永无止境的朝九晚五吗？ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快节奏玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在可破坏的办公室环境中，体验快节奏、混乱激烈的动作战斗。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/d02d8364bc1c29c60e060edbdb2d4d59.poster.avif?t=1770962061\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/d02d8364bc1c29c60e060edbdb2d4d59.webm?t=1770962061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/d02d8364bc1c29c60e060edbdb2d4d59.mp4?t=1770962061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>合成系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把日常办公用品组合起来，打造出荒诞又致命的毁灭工具。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/c307049880c51cc137825db75a74bf6c.poster.avif?t=1770962061\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/c307049880c51cc137825db75a74bf6c.webm?t=1770962061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/c307049880c51cc137825db75a74bf6c.mp4?t=1770962061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>高管指令（增益）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忍受高管们的强行指令——这些强力增益同时伴随着混乱和毁灭性的副作用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/1dc450c64b189e324c836a1a1865eb69.poster.avif?t=1770962061\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/1dc450c64b189e324c836a1a1865eb69.webm?t=1770962061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/1dc450c64b189e324c836a1a1865eb69.mp4?t=1770962061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>职业（职业选择）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的职业，一路打拼，成为终极打工人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/8f565bb817a80d8bdc29afad49ff167a.poster.avif?t=1770962061\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/8f565bb817a80d8bdc29afad49ff167a.webm?t=1770962061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305970/extras/8f565bb817a80d8bdc29afad49ff167a.mp4?t=1770962061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入企业混乱之中 !</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃离疯狂，或者成为这座地狱办公楼的永久员工。游戏风格讽刺，玩法节奏快且高度自定义，《星期一综合症》把日常打工变成了一场恶魔级的屠杀盛宴。准备好迎接你人生中最硬核的职场大战吧。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 土耳其语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 阿拉伯语, 日语, 俄语, 简体中文, 保加利亚语, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 匈牙利语, 印度尼西亚语, 韩语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 瑞典语, 泰语, 繁体中文, 乌克兰语, 越南语, 茨瓦纳语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
